x4freetext: Self supporting enriched 112Sn target of thickness
placed side by side covering a total angular range of
~76 degree have been used inside a 1.5 m diameter
scattering chamber were used to detect different
breakup fragments in coincidence. Each strip
telescope consists of two double-sided Si strip
detectors, with thickness of ~50-60 um as delta E and
1500 um as E respectively. Each detector has 16
vertical and 16 horizontal strips covering an active
Two Silicon surface barrier detectors of
thickness 1 mm were placed at +/- 20 degree wrt beam
direction for normalization and beam monitoring.
barrier detector with delta E ~50 um and E ~ 1000-200
um thick to measure elastic and inclusive alpha
